The '''Fountain''' was a restaurant on [[Drall (planet)|Drall]] in the [[Luminous Gardens]] health spa visited by [[Mara Jade Skywalker]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] in [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]].

They sold a dessert called the [[Fruit Mountain]] which was too large for one woman to finish alone.

